♪I've no longer had a home♪

00:14:05.500 --> 00:14:08.700
♪Magnolia petals fly across the sky♪

00:14:09.580 --> 00:14:12.660
♪Spring and autumn come and go♪

00:14:13.860 --> 00:14:14.980
♪People gather and part♪

00:14:16.220 --> 00:14:20.820
♪How brave can one be with no regrets?♪

00:14:21.780 --> 00:14:25.620
♪I will paint love and hate in the sky♪

00:14:26.980 --> 00:14:29.820
♪Engraving my love for you♪

00:14:30.580 --> 00:14:32.580
♪I roam through this chaotic world♪

00:14:33.340 --> 00:14:38.220
♪Who will guard me for life?♪

00:14:38.940 --> 00:14:42.820
♪I will turn these years into poems♪

00:14:43.620 --> 00:14:46.500
♪Waiting for the flowers and full moon♪

00:14:47.220 --> 00:14:49.740
